======================================================================
Unicode::Map
======================================================================
For binding windows-1259 encoding map file to Unicode::Map
copy CP1259.map to perl/site/lib/Unicode/Map/MS/WIN/ and add to file
perl/site/lib/Unicode/Map/REGISTRY following lines:

   name:    CP1259
   map:     $UnicodeMappings/MS/WIN/CP1259.map
   alias:   windows-1259



======================================================================
XML::Parser::Expat
======================================================================
For binding windows-1259 encoding map file to XML::Parser::Expat
copy CP1259.map to perl/site/lib/XML/Parser/Encodings/

